item.title: Arithmetic Slices
item.description: LeetCode 413. Arithmetic Slices Given an m x n matrix of non-negative integers representing the height of each unit cell in a continent, the “Pacific ocean” touches the left and top edges of the matrix and the “Atlantic ocean” touches the right and bottom edges.
